1 Month Ago Recall that in August, SaharaReporters revealed how Daura was flown to the United Kingdom for urgent medical treatment over an undisclosed ailment. He was said to have been flown in a private jet to the UK after exhibiting respiratory difficulties with symptoms similar to Coronavirus. He is said to have had a history of renal crisis and had regularly visited the West for medical attention. See Also






